#!/usr/bin/env php
1) Login to your hosting account to obtain FTP/SFTP (herein "(S)FTP") credentials.
2) Access your site via (S)FTP to find the file containing this snippet.
3) Download the file.
4) Remove either of the snippets referenced above in "FULL_CODE".
5) Save changes.
6) Upload the file back to your site.
7) Change all access credentials to your applications, including Wordpress/Drupal/Joomla!/etc admin pages, MySQL databases,
    SSH users (if enabled), and (S)FTP credentials.
8) Be extra vigilent for any suspicious activity on your site for the next week.
